          <title>
            <string language="en">Competitive inhibition of the enzyme succinic dehydrogenase by malonic acid</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Konkurrierende Hemmung der Bernstein- 
Dehydrogenase des Enzyms durch malonsauer Säure</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Inhibition concurrentielle de la déshydrogénase
succinique d'enzymes par l'acide malonique</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Inibição do competidor do dehydrogenase 
succinic do enzyme pelo ácido malonic</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Inibizione competitiva della deidrogenasi 
succinica degli enzimi da acido malonico</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ανταγωνιστική παρεμπόδιση της ενζυμικής succinic 
διυδρογενάσης από το μηλονικό οξύ</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Inhibición competitiva del dehydrogenase 
succínico de la enzima por el ácido malonic</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the equation for the competitive inhibition of the enzyme, succinic dehydrogenase, by malonic acid which structurally resemble the substrate, succinic acid, forming the fumaric acid.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die Gleichung für die 
konkurrierende Hemmung des Enzyms, Bernstein- Dehydrogenase, durch 
malonsauer Säure welche strukturell dem Substrat ähneln, die 
Bernstein- Säure und bildet die Fumarsäure.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre l'équation pour 
l'inhibition concurrentielle de l'enzyme, déshydrogénase succinique,
par l'acide malonique ce qui ressemblent structurellement au substrat,
acide succinique, formant l'acide fumarique.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra a equação para a 
inibição do competidor do enzyme, dehydrogenase succinic, pelo 
ácido malonic quais se assemelham estrutural à carcaça, ácido 
succinic, dando forma ao ácido fumaric.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra l'equazione per 
l'inibizione competitiva dell'enzima, deidrogenasi succinica, da acido
malonico quale assomigliano strutturalmente al substrato, acido 
succinico, formante l'acido fumarico.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει την εξίσωση για την 
ανταγωνιστική παρεμπόδιση του ενζύμου, succinic διυδρογενάση, 
από το μηλονικό οξύ που δομικά μοιάζουν με το υπόστρωμα, 
succinic οξύ, που διαμορφώνει το fumaric οξύ.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra la ecuación para la 
inhibición competitiva de la enzima, dehydrogenase succínico, por el
ácido malonic cuáles se asemejan estructural al substrato, ácido 
succínico, formando el ácido fumaric.</string>
          </description>
